    "Founded in 1935, Menora Mivtachim manages more than ILS 375 billion and is one of the country's largest institutional financial players.",
    "Tali and her sister, Niva Gurevitch, inherited their father's controlling stake after his passing in 2013.",
    "Each sister owns about &#8531; of the company, which has paid then more than $300 million dividends since 2014. Tali's husband, Eran Griffel, is chairman of Menora Mivtachim."
